              "path": [
                "hunts",
                ":hunt_id",
                "artifacts",
                ":artifact_id"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Download one forged file \u2014 resolved from the artifact store (Alibaba OSS in prod, disk\noffline; legacy rows carry the bytes inline), with the right content-type and a filename.\nArtifacts are immutable so we issue a strong ETag and honor If-None-Match \u2192 304."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Ask Alpha  [POST]",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/hunts/{hunt_id}/ask",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "hunts",
                ":hunt_id",
                "ask"
              ]
            },
            "description": "The ONE Alpha side-chat, now a smart dispatcher: it classifies each message against the live\nhunt state and either answers, refines the brief in place, steers a running hunt, or launches a\nscoped follow-up \u2014 then replies in Alpha's voice. Multi-turn; carries the full history.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"question\": \"<value>\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {}\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Ask Stream  [POST]",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/hunts/{hunt_id}/ask/stream",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "hunts",
                ":hunt_id",
                "ask",
                "stream"
              ]
            },
            "description": "SSE variant of the smart dispatcher: classify the message against live hunt state, take the\naction (refine / steer / follow-up hunt), THEN stream Alpha's reply and emit the action + any new\nhunt_id on the `done` frame so the frontend can refresh the brief or track the sub-hunt.",
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"question\": \"<value>\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {}\n  ]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
